title: Bratislava: Yoga, meditation & aromatherapy
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
American Talley Sjoberg Varney, who lives in Slovakia, has been a practitioner in aromatherapy for about 10 years. How can aromatherapy help us? Talley also talks about yoga, meditation, and their benefits. Namaste! 
 
Presenter: Anna Fay
